<h2>Overview</h2>

<p>
Riverbend University is the city's largest higher education institution
and a major research center for the region.
</p>

<h2>Founded</h2>

<p>Established in 1898.</p>

<h2>Campus</h2>

<p>
The campus is located in the University Quarter near the Silver River.
It includes modern research laboratories, libraries,
student housing, and athletic facilities.
</p>

<h2>Students</h2>

<p>
Approximately 28,000 undergraduate and graduate students attend the university.
</p>

